gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Spurs 104, Suns 102
gameRecap.excerpt: The Spurs defeated the Suns, 104-102. Jeremy Sochan recorded 26 points and a career-high 18 rebounds for the Spurs, with Devin Vassell adding 26 points, seven assists, and four rebounds in the victory. Devin Booker tallied 36 points, six rebounds, and four assists for the Suns in the losing effort. The Spurs improve to 16-56, while the Suns fall to 42-30.
